'''原孢囊藻属'''（學名：{{lang|la|[[Prototheca|Prototheca]]}}）<ref>Krüger, W. (1894). Kurze Charakteristik einiger niedrerer Organismen im Saftfluss der Laubbäume. Hedwigia 33: 241-266.</ref>是[[綠藻|綠藻]]的一个属，归类於[[綠藻門|綠藻門]][[共球藻綱|共球藻綱]][[小球藻目|小球藻目]][[小球藻科|小球藻科]]。

本属物种目前被归类为[[绿藻|绿藻]]，但它们都因丧失了[[叶绿体|叶绿体]]而失去[[光合作用|光合作用]]能力，必须[[寄生|寄生]]于其他生物。某些[[原孢囊藻|原孢囊藻]]可导致动物和人类疾病，称[[原孢囊藻病|原孢囊藻病]]。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://cmr.asm.org/content/20/2/230|title=Cornelia Lass-Flörl, Astrid Mayr, Clinical Microbiology Reviews Apr 2007, 20 (2) 230-242; DOI: 10.1128/CMR.00032-06|access-date=2021-02-23|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903092300/https://cmr.asm.org/content/20/2/230|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Prototheca webpage|url=https://mycology.adelaide.edu.au/descriptions/prototheca/|access-date=2021-02-23|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224162836/https://mycology.adelaide.edu.au/descriptions/prototheca/|dead-url=no}}</ref>严重感染可导致败血症而致死。<ref>{{cite book|title=Herold S, Klodt T, Toelle D, Dennebaum M, Lippe E, Walz C, Kaes J, Kreft A, Siegel E, Munder M, Teschner D. Lethal systemic and brain infection caused by Prototheca zopfii algae in a patient with acute myeloid leukemia. Med Mycol Case Rep. 2021 Jan 28;32:17-20. doi: 10.1016/j.mmcr.2021.01.004. PMID 33604236;PMCID:PMC7873573.|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7873573/#bib6
}}</ref>

==語源==
原孢囊藻的學名''{{lang|la|Prototheca}}''來自於[[拉丁語|拉丁語]] ''{{lang|la|proto- }}''（意为“原始”）和''{{lang|la|theca }}''（意为“囊”）。

